(282, 1, '2014-11-27 01:57:08', '2014-11-27 01:57:08', '<p>[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1557127486482{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_column][st_search_form_new_single_location form_type=\"mix\" service_items=\"%5B%7B%22tab_title%22%3A%22Hotel%22%2C%22tab_service%22%3A%22st_hotel%22%7D%5D\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1557137504518{margin-top: 80px !important;margin-bottom: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"7/12\"][st_overview_new title=\"Over View\" link=\"url:%23|title:Read%20more||\" image=\"8371\" content_over=\"Virginia Beach is an independent city located in the U.S. state of Virginia. As of the 2010 census, the population was 437,994. In 2013, the population was estimated to be 448,479. It is the most populous city in Virginia as well as the 39th most populous in the United States.</p>\r\n<p>Located on the Atlantic Ocean at the mouth of the Chesapeake Bay, Virginia Beach is included in the Hampton Roads metropolitan area. This area, known as ``America\'s First Region``, also includes the independent cities of Chesapeake, Hampton, Newport News, Norfolk, Portsmouth, and Suffolk, as well as other smaller cities, counties, and towns of Hampton Roads.</p>\r\n<p>Virginia Beach is a resort city with miles of beaches and hundreds of hotels, motels, and restaurants along its oceanfront. Every year the city hosts the East Coast Surfing Championships as well as the North American Sand Soccer Championship, a beach soccer tournament. It is also home to several state parks, several long-protected beach areas, three military bases, a number of large corporations, two universities, International headquarters and site of the television broadcast studios for Pat Robertson\'s Christian Broadcasting Network (CBN), Edgar Cayce\'s Association for Research and Enlightenment, and numerous historic sites. Near the point where the Chesapeake Bay and the Atlantic Ocean meet, Cape Henry was the site of the first landing of the English colonists, who eventually settled in Jamestown, on April 26, 1607.</p>\r\n<p>The city is listed in the Guinness Book of Records as having the longest pleasure beach in the world. It is located at the southern end of the Chesapeake Bay Bridge-Tunnel, the longest bridge-tunnel complex in the world.\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"5/12\"][vc_single_image image=\"7955\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_separator css=\".vc_custom_1557213917472{margin-bottom: 53px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][st_tab_service_location service_tab=\"%5B%7B%22tab_title%22%3A%22Hotel%22%2C%22tab_service%22%3A%22st_hotel%22%7D%5D\" posts_per_page=\"8\" service=\"%5B%7B%22tab_title%22%3A%22Hotel%22%2C%22tab_service%22%3A%22st_hotel%22%7D%2C%7B%22tab_title%22%3A%22Rental%22%2C%22tab_service%22%3A%22st_rental%22%7D%2C%7B%22tab_title%22%3A%22Activity%22%2C%22tab_service%22%3A%22st_activity%22%7D%2C%7B%22tab_title%22%3A%22Tour%22%2C%22tab_service%22%3A%22st_tours%22%7D%5D\" title_tab=\"Explore the Tour\"][vc_empty_space height=\"170px\" el_class=\"space-170\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]The City Maps[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]LUANCH MAPS VIEW[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" row_fullwidth=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1557476683429{margin-top: 64px !important;margin-bottom: 80px !important;}\" el_class=\"top-30\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1557470828724{padding-right: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}\"][vc_gmaps link=\"#E-8_\" size=\"650\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]Trip Ideas[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][st_list_post_ccv ids_post=\"7997,7987\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'Virginia Beach', 'Virginia Beach is an independent city located in the U.S.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'virginia-beach-hotels', '', '', '2020-08-13 06:45:29', '2020-08-13 06:45:29', ''